			<action-date date="20120628">June 28, 2012</action-date>
			<action-desc><sponsor name-id="S309">Mr. Casey</sponsor> introduced the
			 following bill; which was read twice and referred to the
			 <committee-name committee-id="SSAS00">Committee on Armed
			 Services</committee-name></action-desc>
